43:19.514 --> 43:22.433
BECKHAM
REAL MADRID

43:56.717 --> 43:58.219
Good morning.

43:58.928 --> 44:02.598
David Beckham is here
because we believe in him as a footballer.

44:02.598 --> 44:05.476
He is a man who is a symbol of our era,

44:05.476 --> 44:08.145
a symbol of post-modernity.

44:09.063 --> 44:13.568
David, welcome to the league of dreams.

47:07.992 --> 47:10.703
We see this gorgeous guy.

47:10.703 --> 47:13.080
A blond guy who is joining our team.

47:13.080 --> 47:14.749
ROBERTO CARLOS
REAL MADRID 1996-2007

47:18.002 --> 47:23.299
Everyone wanted to have his haircut.

47:23.299 --> 47:26.844
But with my curly hair...

47:26.844 --> 47:28.804
RONALDO NÁZARIO
REAL MADRID 2002-2007

47:28.804 --> 47:34.143
...it was more difficult for me
